Redistribution Conditions

1. Redistribution as an archived file

If you redistribute canna-med as an archived file, the entire contents
of this distribution (COPYRIHGT.canadamed.ja, INSTALL.fbsd.ja and
canadamed.cbd, canadamed.cld, medx.cbd, medx.cld, medinst.cbd,
medinst.cld, henkaku.cbd, henkaku.cld, oldchar.cbd, oldchar.cld and/or
canadasfx.ctd) must be distributed. You cannot modifiy any of the
files.

2. Redistribution in embedded system

If you redistribute canna-med in embedded system, the dictionary files
of this distribution (canadamed.cbd, canadamed.cld, medx.cbd,
medx.cld, medinst.cbd, medinst.cld, henkaku.cbd, henkaku.cld,
oldchar.cbd, oldchar.cld and/or canadasfx.ctd) must be placed on
single directory without any modification. COPYRIGHT.canadamed.ja
must be present in that directory with the right permission for
users to read.

3. Redistribution as a binary package

If you redistribute canna-med as a binary package, the dictionary files
of this distribution (canadamed.cbd, canadamed.cld, medx.cbd,
medx.cld, medinst.cbd, medinst.cld, henkaku.cbd, henkaku.cld,
oldchar.cbd, oldchar.cld and/or canadasfx.ctd) must be placed on
single directory without any modification. COPYRIGHT.canadamed.ja
must be present in that directory with the right permission for
users to read.

Users are strongly advised to download the latest distribution
from the official site. (http://spica.onh.go.jp/med_dic/)
